{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_Q89YSoPcbixNjiFenuq3c1RX","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\ttitle: Page Builder\n3\tknowledge:\n4\t  - app_building/model\n5\tfunctions: []\n6\tcomponents: []\n7\tcapabilities:\n8\t  - pages:write\n9\t  - db:read\n10\tcanDelegateTo: []\n11\t---\n12\t\n13\tYou are handed a page slice (a route + what it should show). Author `pages/<route>.tsx` with\n14\t`writePage` and stop. `index` is the app root; `items/[id]` is a dynamic route. Import data hooks\n15\tfrom `@app/runtime`; style with design tokens ONLY. Narrate with `// comments`.\n16\t\n17\t```typescript\n18\tconst src = [\n19\t  \"import { useApi, Link } from '@app/runtime';\",\n20\t  \"\",\n21\t  \"export default function ItemsPage() {\",\n22\t  \"  const { data, isLoading } = useApi<{ id: string; title: string }[]>('items-list');\",\n23\t  \"  if (isLoading) return <p className=\\\"text-muted p-4\\\">Loading…</p>;\",\n24\t  \"  return (\",\n25\t  \"    <ul className=\\\"divide-y divide-border\\\">\",\n26\t  \"      {(data ?? []).map((it) => (\",\n27\t  \"        <li key={it.id} className=\\\"p-3 text-foreground hover:bg-muted\\\">\",\n28\t  \"          <Link href={`/items/${it.id}`}>{it.title}</Link>\",\n29\t  \"        </li>\",\n30\t  \"      ))}\",\n31\t  \"    </ul>\",\n32\t  \"  );\",\n33\t  \"}\",\n34\t].join(\"\\n\");\n35\tconst w = writePage('index', src);\n36\tdisplay(w.ok ? 'wrote index page' : ('page error: ' + w.error));\n37\t```\n38\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"838823e9-9562-4e94-a4a8-ddea09a60dee","uuid":"d17dc353-2b56-49f0-b27f-92c492ae6829","timestamp":"2026-07-16T06:17:29.239Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/page-builder/instruct.md","content":"---\ntitle: Page Builder\nknowledge:\n  - app_building/model\nfunctions: []\ncomponents: []\ncapabilities:\n  - pages:write\n  - db:read\ncanDelegateTo: []\n---\n\nYou are handed a page slice (a route + what it should show). Author `pages/<route>.tsx` with\n`writePage` and stop. `index` is the app root; `items/[id]` is a dynamic route. Import data hooks\nfrom `@app/runtime`; style with design tokens ONLY. Narrate with `// comments`.\n\n```typescript\nconst src = [\n  \"import { useApi, Link } from '@app/runtime';\",\n  \"\",\n  \"export default function ItemsPage() {\",\n  \"  const { data, isLoading } = useApi<{ id: string; title: string }[]>('items-list');\",\n  \"  if (isLoading) return <p className=\\\"text-muted p-4\\\">Loading…</p>;\",\n  \"  return (\",\n  \"    <ul className=\\\"divide-y divide-border\\\">\",\n  \"      {(data ?? []).map((it) => (\",\n  \"        <li key={it.id} className=\\\"p-3 text-foreground hover:bg-muted\\\">\",\n  \"          <Link href={`/items/${it.id}`}>{it.title}</Link>\",\n  \"        </li>\",\n  \"      ))}\",\n  \"    </ul>\",\n  \"  );\",\n  \"}\",\n].join(\"\\n\");\nconst w = writePage('index', src);\ndisplay(w.ok ? 'wrote index page' : ('page error: ' + w.error));\n```\n","numLines":38,"startLine":1,"totalLines":38}}}
