{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_GHGVz3w5LH3A5w2FTCkyenKh","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\ttitle: API Author\n3\tknowledge:\n4\t  - app_building/model\n5\tfunctions: []\n6\tcomponents: []\n7\tcapabilities:\n8\t  - api:write\n9\t  - db:read\n10\tcanDelegateTo: []\n11\t---\n12\t\n13\tYou are handed an endpoint slice (a route WITH its method, e.g. `items-list/GET`, plus its\n14\tpurpose). Author the handler with `writeApi` and stop. Export `name`, `description`, `Input`,\n15\t`Output`, and a default async handler using `ctx.db`. Narrate with `// comments`.\n16\t\n17\t```typescript\n18\tconst src = [\n19\t  \"export const name = 'items-list';\",\n20\t  \"export const description = 'List all items, newest first.';\",\n21\t  \"export interface Input {}\",\n22\t  \"export interface Output { items: { id: string; title: string }[] }\",\n23\t  \"export default async function handler(_input: Input, ctx: { db: any }): Promise<Output> {\",\n24\t  \"  const items = await ctx.db.query('items', { orderBy: { column: 'createdAt', dir: 'desc' } });\",\n25\t  \"  return { items };\",\n26\t  \"}\",\n27\t].join(\"\\n\");\n28\tconst w = writeApi('items-list/GET', src);\n29\tdisplay(w.ok ? 'wrote items-list GET' : ('api error: ' + w.error));\n30\t```\n31\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"838823e9-9562-4e94-a4a8-ddea09a60dee","uuid":"3f51411f-f56d-4626-b9ea-b6dc8938f699","timestamp":"2026-07-16T06:17:29.369Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/api-author/instruct.md","content":"---\ntitle: API Author\nknowledge:\n  - app_building/model\nfunctions: []\ncomponents: []\ncapabilities:\n  - api:write\n  - db:read\ncanDelegateTo: []\n---\n\nYou are handed an endpoint slice (a route WITH its method, e.g. `items-list/GET`, plus its\npurpose). Author the handler with `writeApi` and stop. Export `name`, `description`, `Input`,\n`Output`, and a default async handler using `ctx.db`. Narrate with `// comments`.\n\n```typescript\nconst src = [\n  \"export const name = 'items-list';\",\n  \"export const description = 'List all items, newest first.';\",\n  \"export interface Input {}\",\n  \"export interface Output { items: { id: string; title: string }[] }\",\n  \"export default async function handler(_input: Input, ctx: { db: any }): Promise<Output> {\",\n  \"  const items = await ctx.db.query('items', { orderBy: { column: 'createdAt', dir: 'desc' } });\",\n  \"  return { items };\",\n  \"}\",\n].join(\"\\n\");\nconst w = writeApi('items-list/GET', src);\ndisplay(w.ok ? 'wrote items-list GET' : ('api error: ' + w.error));\n```\n","numLines":31,"startLine":1,"totalLines":31}}}
