{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_SZXB2YyucfDUA4Xcjjx9DgkN","type":"tool_result","content":"{\n  \"seq\": 1079,\n  \"event\": {\n    \"ts\": 1784184242379,\n    \"type\": \"yield\",\n    \"context\": \"fork:build_app\",\n    \"nodeId\": \"fork_96_47c91784\",\n    \"kind\": \"delegate\",\n    \"args\": [\n      \"system-appbuilder\",\n      \"automator\",\n      \"build_live_project\",\n      {\n        \"query\": \"Organize the Tanzania trip material into an app the user can open on their phone. The material covers: (1) trip itinerary/plan with dates, flights, safari booking, contacts; (2) trip costs from a spreadsheet — seed every row into the database; (3) Ngorongoro park fee tariff details; (4) a Stone Town Zanzibar photo memory; (5) crater-day voice note with driver Emmanuel, bracelet purchase (~$20-25/~35,000 TZS), ranger tip (~5,000 TZS cash at gate), and a reminder to ask Richard about the tip before the safari balance payment. Build per-topic specialist spaces for each distinct topic so the user can ask plain questions later.\\n\\nBuild the complete live-project app now: write source-derived tables and rows, then write the project API and openable pages that show those rows.\\n\\nSource summary:\\nThree files: tanzaniamemories.md (trip itinerary, Aug 3-20 2026, Cairo→Arusha→3-day Suricata Safaris group camping safari, fully booked), trip-costs.xlsx (all expenses with categories and payment status), ngorongoro-conservation-area-tariffs.pdf (official park fees). One image: stone-town-zanzibar.jpg (courtyard photo in Stone Town). One voice note transcript: Ngorongoro crater day, driver Emmanuel, bought 2 beaded bracelets from a Maasai lady for ~$20-25 / ~35,000 TZS, Emmanuel mentioned extra ranger tip ~5,000 TZS cash at gate separate from park fees, user wants to ask Richard about it before safari balance payment.\\n\\nFacts available only from image/audio analysis:\\nImage (stone-town-zanzibar.jpg): The photo looks up into a bright interior courtyard of a multi-story building, likely a hotel or apartment complex, with white stucco walls, arched windows, and several dark carved wooden balconies stacked along the facade. The architecture has an ornate, Middle Eastern or Mediterranean feel, and there are no people or readable signs visible. | Voice note transcript: Ngorongoro crater day, driver guide Emmanuel (not Richard from the office), Maasai lady sold 2 beaded bracelets to Athina Mari for ~$20-25 (~35,000 TZS), Emmanuel mentioned extra ranger tip ~5,000 TZS cash at gate separate from park fees — user wants to ask Richard about this before safari balance payment.\\n\\nSpecialist build results:\\n[{\\\"topic\\\":\\\"Tanzania Safari — Northern Circuit (Ngorongoro, Serengeti, Manyara)\\\",\\\"ok\\\":true,\\\"errors\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"topic\\\":\\\"Stone Town, Zanzibar\\\",\\\"ok\\\":true,\\\"errors\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"topic\\\":\\\"Cairo Stopover\\\",\\\"ok\\\":true,\\\"errors\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\n        \"context\": {\n          \"attachmentIds\": [\n            \"c7d674e0-3b6e-4673-a499-2fb80290b706\",\n            \"0b2c022e-ae6e-48e7-a657-9ac9a97cc7b6\",\n            \"99b08c91-37e9-4ddf-8564-f2f848eeb8cd\",\n            \"66244f0a-c50e-4e74-95c9-7b034685c690\"\n          ]\n        },\n        \"attachmentIds\": [\n          \"c7d674e0-3b6e-4673-a499-2fb80290b706\",\n          \"0b2c022e-ae6e-48e7-a657-9ac9a97cc7b6\",\n          \"99b08c91-37e9-4ddf-8564-f2f848eeb8cd\",\n          \"66244f0a-c50e-4e74-95c9-7b034685c690\"\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"yieldId\": \"fork_96_47c91784_y1\"\n  }\n}\n{\n  \"seq\": 1085,\n  \"event\": {\n    \"ts\": 1784184245960,\n    \"type\": \"yield\",\n    \"context\": \"delegate:system-appbuilder/automator/build_live_project\",\n    \"nodeId\": \"delegate_97_d105354f\",\n    \"kind\": \"tasklist\",\n    \"args\": [\n      \"build_live_project\",\n      {\n        \"query\": \"Organize the Tanzania trip material into an app the user can open on th